<p>On Nova's Matt, Sarah and Matty J show, the 33-year-old explained that he broke up a fight after two young guys tackled an elderly couple. </p>

<p>Hero move: On Nova's Matt, Sarah and Matty J show, Matty J (pictured) explained that he broke up a fight after two young guys tackled an elderly couple</p>

<p>'I’m looking around, the park is really busy, everyone is frozen and shocked,' he said. </p>

